cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.CR 

The paper deals with activity recognition, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). The use of regular expressions to discover patterns in activities suggests a possible connection to information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the detection of anomalies in activity streams could be related to computer security (cs.CR).
